{"tid":844442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【醜出國際】中國大叔花園大解 非洲漢質問：你喺自己國家會隨地屙？","createTime":"2018-10-02T01:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T04:57:06.000Z","uid":92301,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1fdf74afaf53053286557eb75a81378b3777f116","tid":844442,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T01:30:31.000Z","msg":"瑞典電視台（SVT）節目「瑞典新聞」早前播出一段短片，「提醒」中國遊客別在瑞典隨地大小便，事件引發中國官方激烈反應，斥責節目突破人類道德底線。言猶在耳，又有中國人在他國隨地便溺。<br />\n<br />\n尼日利亞傳媒「pulse」日前報道，有網民在Instagram上載影片，指一名身在非洲國家加納的中國男子在一花園大便。片中見該中年男子將長褲褪至小腿，然後蹲在草叢中大便。當地人發現後立即上前喝止，並聲言要報警。<br />\n<br />\n大便男見醜行被發現，即時匆匆用紙巾清潔，再尷尬走出草叢並穿回長褲，又連番說：「Sorry，sorry(對不起，對不起)。」當地民眾拿起鐵鏟，要求大便男清理糞便，更質問對方會否在自己國家隨地便溺，不過大便男未有正面回應，繼續用鏟清理糞便然後離開。<br />\n<br />\n另有報道指，近年到加納的中國人數目大增，呼籲政府有必要正視此類問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180930/58739615\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F58739615&d=P1GZ2xwQnzPT8eOpEw7DJ49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=b5c19135\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180930%2F58739615&h=e083797a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180930/58739615</a>"},{"pid":"b85fe8ee6ed186e7153059d263f86bffde746071","tid":844442,"uid":195728,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T01:31:22.000Z","msg":"會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e3205dad74ed2130dd1f9faaf649b8d8a6315f","tid":844442,"uid":136987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T01:32:49.000Z","msg":"點解一定要隨地拉屎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"594d259108e59d6c9789738f2d8718d7af128387","tid":844442,"uid":35014,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T01:33:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cd92f56712774d58c